### Remote CRUD E2E (VS Code REST Client)
### Run requests top-to-bottom so response references are available.
### Override apiBaseUrl with your deployed mock API base URL.

@apiBaseUrl = https://your-api-name.region.azurecontainerapps.io
@resource = products

### 1) GET list
# @name getList
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/api/{{resource}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 2) GET existing record by id=1
# @name getOne
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/api/{{resource}}/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 3) POST create
# @name createItem
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/api/{{resource}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Widget",
  "price": 5.0,
  "category": "test",
  "in_stock": true
}

###

### 4) GET created record (id from POST)
# @name getCreated
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/api/{{resource}}/{{createItem.response.body.$.id}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 5) PATCH created record (id from POST)
# @name patchCreated
PATCH {{apiBaseUrl}}/api/{{resource}}/{{createItem.response.body.$.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "price": 7.5
}

###

### 6) DELETE created record (id from POST)
# @name deleteCreated
DELETE {{apiBaseUrl}}/api/{{resource}}/{{createItem.response.body.$.id}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 7) GET deleted record (should be 404)
# @name getDeleted
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/api/{{resource}}/{{createItem.response.body.$.id}}
Accept: application/json
